{"tid":998065,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"三後衞高汁文！變幻原是永恆：三後衛如何變化適應戰術 | 譯：雯B","createTime":"2019-01-27T16:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T16:10:39.000Z","uid":137897,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4e790d6e4d5c99cc50d690bdbc9eebce84a47e54","tid":998065,"uid":137897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:10:39.000Z","msg":"在2014年的世界盃，出現一股逆潮流：4後衛不再是常用陣式。當2010年世界盃大家都用上4後衛去擺出一個防守陣型時，大家都會以為4後衛已是世界常態。<br />\n但南美的智利使用3後衛打出穩定的表現，墨西哥與阿根廷，甚至打入四強的荷蘭使用一個變換的4後衛，而烏拉圭與哥斯達黎加也是用上5後防。這篇寫於2014年7月的文章將會解釋3後衛的配置，當中的細節安排與走動，戰術長處與特色、弱點與反擊的配置。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sportsyeah.hk/2019/01/27/%e8%ae%8a%e5%b9%bb%e5%8e%9f%e6%98%af%e6%b0%b8%e6%81%86%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%89%e5%be%8c%e8%a1%9b%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e8%ae%8a%e5%8c%96%e9%81%a9%e6%87%89%e6%88%b0%e8%a1%93-%e8%ad%af%ef%bc%9a%e9%9b%afb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportsyeah.hk%2F2019%2F01%2F27%2F%25e8%25ae%258a%25e5%25b9%25bb%25e5%258e%259f%25e6%2598%25af%25e6%25b0%25b8%25e6%2581%2586%25ef%25bc%259a%25e4%25b8%2589%25e5%25be%258c%25e8%25a1%259b%25e5%25a6%2582%25e4%25bd%2595%25e8%25ae%258a%25e5%258c%2596%25e9%2581%25a9%25e6%2587%2589%25e6%2588%25b0%25e8%25a1%2593-%25e8%25ad%25af%25ef%25bc%259a%25e9%259b%25afb%2F&d=RFvMBDugZ9Q5DE7FF%2B10mxxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=578e7565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.sportsyeah.hk/2019/01/27/%e8%ae%8a%e5%b9%bb%e5%8e%9f%e6%98%af%e6%b0%b8%e6%81%86%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%89%e5%be%8c%e8%a1%9b%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e8%ae%8a%e5%8c%96%e9%81%a9%e6%87%89%e6%88%b0%e8%a1%93-%e8%ad%af%ef%bc%9a%e9%9b%afb/</a><br />\n<br />\n🖕🏽🖕🏽🖕🏽<br />\n詳細內容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}